OL,3,CTraumatised friends of drowning
OL,4,Cvictim: 'Don't go near the water'
OL,6,FFriends of a teenager who drowned in
OL,7,FWest Yorkshire have warned others
OL,8,Fnever to enter open water.
OL,10,FTyler Wilson, who was 16, was with
OL,11,Fschool friends when he jumped into the
OL,12,Friver Calder in Methley in May last
OL,13,Fyear. His body was recovered 90
OL,14,Fminutes later.
OL,16,FHis friends say they are traumatised
OL,17,Ffrom what happened, some even avoiding
OL,18,Fgoing to the swimming baths.
