OL,6,FTyler's family unveiled a plaque and
OL,7,Femergency throwline at the site where
OL,8,Fhe drowned over the weekend.
OL,10,FHis granddad Michael Scott said: ''I
OL,11,Fstill don't have the words to describe
OL,12,Fwhat happened. He's in my head when I
OL,13,Fwake up and when I go to bed at night.
OL,14,FI used to play in open water as a kid
OL,15,Fand I regret that now. Just use your
OL,16,Flocal baths. It's not worth it.''
OL,18,FHe's now teamed up with Simon
OL,19,FHaycock's family, whose son Sam also
OL,20,Fdrowned in Ulley reservoir in
OL,21,FRotherham three years ago.
