OL,6,FSimon's charity, Sam's Army, has
OL,7,Fraised the funds for the new lifeline,
OL,8,Fthe only one in West Yorkshire.
OL,10,FSimon said: "There's not enough of
OL,11,Fthese throwline stations, there's
OL,12,Floads and loads of open water like
OL,13,Fthis, that hasn't got any equipment
OL,14,Fnear them at all and it at least gives
OL,15,Fthem a chance that there's something
OL,16,Fif they need it."
OL,18,FThe Lowland Rescue team were also at
OL,19,Fthe event, to teach Tyler's friends
OL,20,Fhow to use the new line.
